item.title: CVE-2022-25942|2024-08-03T04:49:44.438Z -- hdf5%20group -- libhdf5
item.description: An out-of-bounds read vulnerability exists in the gif2h5 functionality of HDF5 Group libhdf5 1.10.4. A specially-crafted GIF file can lead to code execution. An attacker can provide a malicious file to trigger this vulnerability.

item.title: CVE-2022-26061|2024-08-03T04:56:37.494Z -- hdf5%20group -- libhdf5
